## Summary

| Area | What exists |
|------|-------------|
| **Sessions / cookies** | TanStack Start `useSession` in `src/server/session.server.ts` — three encrypted `httpOnly` cookies: `__session` (account id), `authToken`, `refreshToken`. |
| **Auth helpers** | `src/lib/auth.ts` (login URL builder, session expiry helpers, safe redirect), `src/types/auth.ts` (session shapes), `src/routes/_login/auth.ts` (server redirect-if-logged-in, client login/signup redirects). |
| **API “client”** | There is **no shared axios/fetch client class**. Server-side Org API access is **`src/server/org-api.server.ts`**: `fetch` to `env.API_HOSTNAME` with `Authorization: Bearer <token>` from the `authToken` session (or `MOCK_ACCESS_TOKEN`). |
| **Who is logged in?** | `src/server/app-bootstrap.ts` calls `/users/me` and `/tenants` via `getOrgApiJson`; `_authed` layout loader uses `getAppBootstrapData()`. |
| **Router / protection** | **`src/routes/_authed.tsx`** loader: no bootstrap → redirect `/login`; optional redirect to `/workspace/new`. Login/signup use **`redirectIfAuthenticated`** in loaders. |
| **Middleware** | **No** Next.js-style or Nitro middleware files in this app. Patterns: **`loader`**, **`beforeLoad`** (one use: `campaigns/new.tsx` redirects), **`createServerFn`** guards. |
| **`app.config.ts`** | **Not present.** **`vite.config.ts`** + **`src/router.tsx`** + file-based routes under `src/routes/`. |
| **OAuth implementation** | **Not in this repo’s `src/`** as route handlers. `buildLoginStartPath` points to **`/oauth/start`**. `docs/README.md` says the **separate auth app** (`AUTH_APP_URL`) does Cognito/OAuth and returns via **`/oauth/callback`**, which sets the cookies described in `session.server.ts`. |

